title: Two Guys Knock Down The Wall with 1 Stick
itunes:title: Two Guys Knock Down The Wall with 1 Stick
description: Today on The Cigar Authority we're smoking the Berlin Wall with Victor Vitale of THE CIGAR AGENCY GLOBAL DISTRIBUTION, and an advance pre-release of American Classic Blend from Alec Bradley as we're joined by Ben & Tyler of 2 Guys1Stick.com. It's time for the finer things in life... It's time for The Cigar Authority.
